&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Staff Nurse to become part of our team within the Endoscopy Unit at Lymington New Forest Hospital. Lymington is a pretty Georgian coastal town on the southern edge of the New Forest, Hampshire.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are currently looking for an enthusiastic and dynamic individual. We are a JAG accredited unit consisting of 2 Endoscopy rooms undertaking diagnostic procedures. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;State of the art decontamination facilities support the unit to work efficiently and consistently meeting standards set by JAG.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are a committed, hardworking and highly motivated individual with the ability to work well within a team environment, have an eagerness to develop new skills and expertise within an Endoscopy Unit, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
